    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3213350/extras/2bb56c89f985a65b018d33f3764b6198.poster.avif?t=1772282880\" ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3213350/extras/2bb56c89f985a65b018d33f3764b6198.webm?t=1772282880\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Venture through working men's club parties, 24-hour all-night shrubberies, A post apocalyptic Peak District and fire-regulation-busting, volcano-adjacent coffee shops in this final comedy point and click extravaganza!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Crammed to breaking point with clever puzzles, hilarious events and  a thoroughly 1990s adventure style.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3213350/extras/10d23e024eba460f58e40f4e3635d7b2.poster.avif?t=1772282880\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3213350/extras/10d23e024eba460f58e40f4e3635d7b2.webm?t=1772282880\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3213350/extras/10d23e024eba460f58e40f4e3635d7b2.mp4?t=1772282880\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3213350/extras/0e3fa3cd9c7e5c982ec5a714c2711780.poster.avif?t=1772282880\" ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3213350/extras/0e3fa3cd9c7e5c982ec5a714c2711780.webm?t=1772282880\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Over 80 unique locations from beautiful Peak district scenery to pirate gambling dens</i></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>1990s style hand-drawn pixel art and several hundred crazy animations</i></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Hours of original and hilarious dialogue across 6~10 hours of playtime (with variable endings)</i></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Find Kluberries in the wilderness and exchange them for 'glimpses into the future' (optional clues)</i></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>A veritable orgy of puzzles and highly original mechanics to keep you scratching your head until it becomes raw and swollen</i></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Fill your very own achievement room with unique gifts and artefacts that link in with your steam achievements across multiple playthroughs</i></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>In-depth and high quality ambient soundscapes and audio</i></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>A live instrument recorded folk/fantasy original soundtrack of over 37 original compositions</i></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3213350/extras/33271c05355d8081ab6b8f25d4517d58.webp?t=1772282880\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3213350/extras/33271c05355d8081ab6b8f25d4517d58.poster.webp?t=1772282880\" class=\"bb_img\" width=800 height=450 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3213350/extras/aa52cf1ec3a071265f4fa6864e09ce5f.poster.avif?t=1772282880\" ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3213350/extras/aa52cf1ec3a071265f4fa6864e09ce5f.webm?t=1772282880\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Renowned for its sharp writing</strong>, originality, absurd humour, and unforgettable musical compositions, the Brownie's Adventure series has reached its beautiful and final “vinegar strokes.”</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Every square pixel</strong> of this hand-drawn finale has been crafted with care, from its fun, intricate puzzles to its sweeping, needlessly rich and epic orchestral soundtrack.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Whether you’re a long-time fan</strong> or delving into the series for the first time, this epic adventure stands on its own while giving an overtly vigorous fist bump to the absolute madness that made it possible.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3213350/extras/0c4166e4a2ed907cf4ef38e200c0720c.poster.avif?t=1772282880\" width=774 height=430 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3213350/extras/0c4166e4a2ed907cf4ef38e200c0720c.webm?t=1772282880\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3213350/extras/0c4166e4a2ed907cf4ef38e200c0720c.mp4?t=1772282880\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>So, gear up and crack on—because if Brownie doesn’t save the world(s), who will? The RSPCA? Ofcom? You, ideally. That would be great. </strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
